didn't like her.

01:22:23.640 --> 01:22:25.205
That's a possibility.

01:22:25.640 --> 01:22:27.319
You know, I have a theory

01:22:27.320 --> 01:22:30.319
that sometimes when
you don't understand

01:22:30.320 --> 01:22:31.679
what the other person is saying,

01:22:31.680 --> 01:22:34.799
